Ursaline Bryant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ursaline_Bryant 0 Ursaline Bryant (born 1947) is an actress who has appeared in several films from the 1970s to 1990s. She played starship Captain Tryla Scott in the Star Trek: The Next Generation episode "Conspiracy". She also had a memorable role as a prostitute in The Golden Girls episode "Ladies of the Evening".
